{"tid":662924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎持刀襲擊案釀2死4傷 目擊者受訪時仍猶有餘悸","createTime":"2018-05-12T22:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T08:54:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f78fa0bca7fd99df173b3fe6489b5bc24d9e8829","tid":662924,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T22:47:10.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎發生持刀襲擊案，一名男子在市中心歌劇院附近，用刀殺死一人，數人受傷，警員到場後將他擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期六晚，警方說5人遇襲，其中一人死亡，4人受傷送院，當中兩人情況嚴重。警方又說暫時未知疑犯身分，亦不知道他行兇的動機。內政部長科隆在社交專頁慰問受害者及家屬，又感謝警方迅速制伏疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者接受訪問時，仍然表現得十分驚慌，表示案發期間途人紛紛走入餐廳或咖啡店躲避。有其他目擊者就說，警員原本想用電槍制伏疑犯，但未能阻止對方，最終開了兩槍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E9%87%802%E6%AD%BB4%E5%82%B7-%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E6%99%82%E4%BB%8D%E7%8C%B6%E6%9C%89%E9%A4%98%E6%82%B8-210859238.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2587%25802%25E6%25AD%25BB4%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%258D%25E7%258C%25B6%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25A4%2598%25E6%2582%25B8-210859238.html&d=D3NCg31tFAP3E2nHj9EEmpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=498efbd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E6%A1%88%E9%87%802%E6%AD%BB4%E5%82%B7-%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E6%99%82%E4%BB%8D%E7%8C%B6%E6%9C%89%E9%A4%98%E6%82%B8-210859238.html</a>"},{"pid":"f90713c470a73e58a93d80d575fad4c2acf7e829","tid":662924,"uid":45077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T23:57:17.000Z","msg":"幾時到中國發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b9ebad5f8870f4bcb90a4622c619d95ea0d5c3","tid":662924,"uid":25858,"